text:
I’m brewing pir & toothy enchantress right now.
- no other pir & toothy enchantress decks
- toothy helps with BOTH wincon & card draw, two weaknesses of the deck
- missing white is kinda sad
Any ideas? My main ones revolve around drawing a ton or cards, even symmetrically like rites of flourishing
A limited number of auras like rancor to help toothy kill stuff
I feel like there's gotta be some interesting counter things that go well with Enchantress. Let me look into it for a minute.

Interesting things with Proliferate and such: [[Simic Ascendancy]], [[As Foretold]], [[Helix Pinnacle]] (probably only if you include some infinite mana), [[Archmage Ascension]], [[Druid's Repository]], [[Mind Unbound]] (maybe with donate effects for when it gets out of hand?), [[Parallax Tide]] (There's some Stax for you), [[Hibernation's End]], [[Iceberg]], [[Private Research]], [[Temporal Distortion]] & [[Freyalise's Winds]] (Another great Stax piece), [[Cyclone]] could be a decent finisher if you find some damage prevention,  and [[Malignant Growth]] if you found a way to go draw punish.
...It would appear I have overloaded scryfall bot.
There's some really interesting stuff I'd never seen before in there, though.
You get Ancestral Mask and Auramancer's Guise so that helps.
Also, looking through that list, I'd never seen [[Mana Vortex]] either. That card is nasty.
